<div id="content">
<h1>Achievement</h1>
<p><em>One of the <a href="../types" title="2A/types">Leap2A item types</a></em></p>
<pre>&lt;rdf:type rdf:resource="leap2:achievement" /&gt; or
&lt;rdf:type rdf:resource="<a href="http://www.cetis.org.uk/leap2/terms/achievement" rel="nofollow">http://www.cetis.org.uk/leap2/terms/achievement</a>" /&gt;   </pre>
<table class="tableGreenBorder">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Definition:</td>
<td>Describes a state of the world that has been brought about at least partly by the agency of the portfolio holder</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Examples:</td>
<td>
<ul>
<li>Qualification, with date of award</li>
<li>Passing a test, with date passed</li>
<li>Winning a competition or race</li>
<li>Achieving a previously set target</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Literals used:</td>
<td>
<ul>
<li><a href="../literals#date" title="2A/literals">date</a> <a href="../literals#point" title="2A/literals">point</a>="<a href="../literals#end" title="2A/literals">end</a>" = the actual date at which the achievement was accomplished</li>
<li><a href="../literals#date" title="2A/literals">date</a> <a href="../literals#point" title="2A/literals">point</a>="<a href="../literals#target" title="2A/literals">target</a>" = the date planned for completion, if wanted for comparison</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Relationships used:</td>
<td>
<ul>
<li><a href="../relationships#has_evidence" title="2A/relationships">has evidence</a> → evidential items</li>
<li><a href="../relationships#is_evidence_of" title="2A/relationships">is evidence of</a> → items that can have evidence</li>
<li><a href="../relationships#reflected_on_by" title="2A/relationships">reflected on by</a> → <a href="../type/entry" title="2A/entry">entry</a></li>
<li><a href="../relationships#is_outcome_of" title="2A/relationships">is outcome of</a> → <a href="../type/activity" title="2A/activity">activity</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Categories:</td>
<td>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://wiki.cetis.org.uk/leap2/a/categories/life_area" title="2A/categories/life area">life area</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Can degrade to:<br /> / inherits from:</td>
<td><a href="http://wiki.cetis.org.uk/leap2/a/type/entry" title="2A/entry">entry</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Notes:</td>
<td>An achievement records actual results rather than what was planned for or aimed at as a goal.
<p>It is less clear whether this should include licences, and if so, what the dates should be. A possibility is to have the start and end dates as the start and end of the licence.</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><br /> See also <a href="http://wiki.cetis.ac.uk/LEAP_achievement" rel="nofollow">earlier ideas on achievement</a></p>

